	<h1 class="title entry-title">A Gentle Introduction to Text Summarization</h1>	</header>
<div class="post-meta"><span class="small">By</span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="fn"><a href="https://machinelearningmastery.com/author/jasonb/" title="Posts by Jason Brownlee" rel="author">Jason Brownlee</a></span></span> <span class="small">on</span> <abbr class="date time published updated" title="2017-11-29T05:00:22+1100">November 29, 2017</abbr>  <span class="small">in</span> <span class="categories"><a href="https://machinelearningmastery.com/category/natural-language-processing/" title="View all items in Deep Learning for Natural Language Processing">Deep Learning for Natural Language Processing</a></span>  </div>
