</ul>
<h2>Summary</h2>
<p>In this post, you discovered the problem of text summarization in natural language processing.</p>
<p>Specifically, you learned:</p>
<ul>
<li>Why text summarization is important, especially given the wealth of text available on the internet.</li>
<li>Examples of text summarization you may encounter every single day.</li>
<li>The application and promise of deep learning methods for automatic text summarization.</li>
</ul>
