		   		<div class="comment-entry">

				<p>Perhaps experiment with a few methods on your dataset and discover what works best?</p>

				
	                <div class="reply">
	                    <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-483524' data-commentid="483524" data-postid="4465" data-belowelement="comment-483524" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Jason Brownlee'>Reply</a>	                </div><!-- /.reply -->

				</div><!-- /comment-entry -->

			</div><!-- /.comment-container -->

	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
</ul><!-- .children -->
</li><!-- #comment-## -->

		<li id="comment-498839" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1">

